n><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/27/02 4:29:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=414.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: StarCraft Ghost</span><hr size=1> Let me begin by saying this game <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> will kick major a$$</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, and will probably, IMO, be the best third-person view shooter to date.  Yes, Ghost isn't a FPS; it is, as Kenny Geeze stated, in third-person view.<br>
<br>
