<br>
As Nova, players will be able to scale fences, hang from wires, climb poles and scale walls, and negotiate tightropes <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Unveil the Next Chapter in the StarCraft Saga</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
