Yes, yes, it makes you want to cry for joy, I know.<br>
<br>
I would like to give my opinion on some of these ideas.  First off, while it does say that you will be able to fight at &quot;sonic speed&quot; by what I have read this is just the same as bullet-speed in Max Payne(a la Matrix).  All I can say is that I hope that this doesn't turn out to just be a rehash of the same idea.  I mean it does get annoying that since the Matrix, every-friggin-thing is using this idea.  I wonder if Blizzard and Nihilistic can make this look a little different......somehow.<br>
<br>
Secondly, I just can't wait to command Battlecruisers and Siege Tanks, and see them in <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> full-scale 3D!!!!</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  Also, the idea of being in the middle of a major war just sends my mind into a tingling spasm!  Just imagine looking to your left and seeing a wave of little zerglings approach you, and then have a team of firebats back you up, beautiful thoughts, just beautiful.<br>
<br>
